16. What are the key factors influencing consumer preferences for iodophor sanitizers?
Consumer preferences for iodophor sanitizers are influenced by factors such as effectiveness, ease of use, compatibility with different surfaces, and safety for food contact applications.

17. How is the iodophor sanitizer market impacted by the COVID-19 pandemic?
The COVID-19 pandemic has led to an increased demand for sanitization products, including iodophor sanitizers, as businesses and individuals seek to maintain hygienic practices to prevent the spread of the virus.

